---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <div class="bg-gray-950 py-20">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 prose prose-invert">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">When Should You Upgrade Your PC vs Buy New in 2026?</h1>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">July 2026 • RigRescue Helpful Tips</p>

            <p>Not sure whether to upgrade your current computer or buy a new one? Here's a practical guide to help you decide.</p>

            <h2>Upgrade If...</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Intel 8th generation or ryzen 2nd generation or newer can upgrade to windows 11!</li>
                <li>You currently have a hard drive instead of solid state</li>
                <li>have at least 8gb of RAM and support for more (for when windows 12 releases)</li>
                <li>You want to game and are only missing a graphics card and upgraded power supply</li>
                <li>Ram is still expensive and you want to stay on older cheaper ram that still performs well!</li>
                <li>You have less than 300 dollars to spend on a new PC</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Buy New If...</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Your system is older than 2018</li>
                <li>You want modern features (Wi-Fi 7, DDR5, etc.)</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Let Us Help</h2>
            <p>RigRescue offers honest advice on part selection, full build services, or remote diagnostics to help you make the smartest choice for your budget.</p>

            <div class="text-center mt-12">
                <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg font-medium">
                    Get Personalized PC Advice
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
